TO: KATHARINE A. WHITE

CC, 1 p.

Ithaca, N.Y.





November 19, 1950

Dear Katharine,

I would be very glad to do an article, or a series of articles, on the lines Ross suggests.1 His idea not only does not clash with mine but rather amplifies it and I think I am the right man for it since I know exactly all the moves in the Soviet anti-Ame